    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies the Simple Control Plane (CP) and User Plane (UP) Separation Broadband Network Gateway (BNG) control channel Protocol (S-CUSP) for communications between a CP and a UP. S-CUSP is designed to be flexible and extensible so as to easily allow for the addition of further messages and data items, should requirements be expressed in the future.</t>
